---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/sections/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/sections/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
import HeroSection from '../components/sections/HeroSection.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark" class="dark">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Organization',
      name: 'Order of the 19th',
      url: new URL('/', Astro.site).toString(),
      logo: new URL('/favicon.svg', Astro.site).toString(),
    })} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <HeroSection
        title="Welcome to the Order of the 19th"
        subtitle="An exclusive society united by tradition, excellence, and the pursuit of the perfect round."
        showCTA
      />
     
      <!-- Expanded What is the Order Section -->
      <section class="py-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="prose prose-invert mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What is the Order of the 19th?</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
            <p class="text-center">
              For centuries, the most important conversations in golf happened not on the course, but afterwards. 
              In clubhouses, taverns, and bars around the world, the <strong class="text-[color:var(--accent)]">19th hole</strong> became 
              where deals were made, friendships forged, and wisdom shared over post-round drinks.
            </p>
            
            <div class="my-8 p-6 bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-xl border-2 border-[color:var(--accent)]/30">
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-center">
                The modern world has changed everything.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-center">
                Today's golfers rush from the 18th green to their cars. The 19th hole sits empty whilst players 
                chase the next tee time or hurry back to endless obligations. The art of the post-round story, 
                the bonds formed through unhurried conversation, these traditions are being lost.
              </p>
            </div>
<p class="text-center">
  The Order of the 19th is a <strong>brotherhood of golfers</strong> dedicated to preserving what makes 
  golf truly timeless. Founded by nineteen individuals who refuse to let the soul of the game disappear, 
  we are building a digital sanctuary where the traditions of the 19th hole live on. Wherever the 19th hole 
  still thrives, there is a good chance an Order member has raised a glass there, our presence is felt, not 
  advertised. From village muni bars to royal clubhouses, our members are present, but never obvious.
</p>

<p class="text-center">
  We trace our lineage to the informal gatherings at St Andrews in the 1500s. For generations, 
  these traditions thrived in clubhouses worldwide. In 2025, we step into the light—preserving 
  centuries of wisdom whilst embracing the digital age.
</p>


<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10 mb-10">
  <div class="text-center p-6 bg-neutral-800/30 rounded-lg border border-[color:var(--accent)]/20">
    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[color:var(--accent)] mb-2">500+</div>
    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Years of Tradition</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center p-6 bg-neutral-800/30 rounded-lg border border-[color:var(--accent)]/20">
    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[color:var(--accent)] mb-2">47</div>
    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Countries with Members</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center p-6 bg-neutral-800/30 rounded-lg border border-[color:var(--accent)]/20">
    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[color:var(--accent)] mb-2">∞</div>
    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Stories to Share</div>
  </div>
</div>


            <p class="text-center text-xl font-medium italic text-[color:var(--accent)]/90">
              We gather not to compete, but to connect. We are the keepers of golf's social soul.
            </p>

            <div class="text-center mt-10">
              <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-[color:var(--accent)] !text-white rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity text-lg font-semibold">
                Discover Our Full History
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Rest of your page continues below -->


      <!-- Navigation Cards -->
      <section class="py-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          
          <!-- Card 1: Founding Members -->
          <a href="/the19" class="block p-8 rounded-2xl border transition-all duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-[#1e1e1e] border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700/50 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] no-underline">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white underline decoration-emerald-500/50">Founding Members</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              Meet the nineteen individuals who established the Order and their unique stories.
            </p>
          </a>
         <!-- Card 2: The Archive -->
          <a href="/archive" class="block p-8 rounded-2xl border transition-all duration-300 bg-white dark:bg-[#1e1e1e] border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700/50 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] no-underline">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white underline decoration-emerald-500/50">The Archive</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              Stories, insights, and adventures from our members on and off the course.
            </p>
          </a>

               </div>
      </section>

    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
